name: Global Webinar on Civil, Architectural, and Environmental Engineering
content: Fratun Meetings extends you the enormous pleasure and the honor of inviting you to attend Global Webinar on Civil, Architectural, and Environmental Engineering (GWCAEE-2022) which will be held during 01-02, March, 2022\. The theme of the virtual event is “New Technologies, Methods and Techniques in Civil, Architectural and Environmental Engineering”. The main intention behind the GWCAEE-2022 is to bring together renowned doctors, scientists, researchers, and scholars from all over the world to exchange their ideas, present sophisticated research works, and discuss the latest advancements in the field of Civil, Architectural, and Environmental Engineering.
